{
  "video_id": "9jRkACywckE",
  "title": "Stanley McChrystal: The military case for sharing knowledge",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12656.0,
      "end_time": 14626.0,
      "text": "When I was a young officer, they told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14626.0,
      "end_time": 16894.0,
      "text": "to follow my instincts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16894.0,
      "end_time": 19150.0,
      "text": "to go with my gut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19150.0,
      "end_time": 21159.0,
      "text": "and what I&#39;ve learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21160.0,
      "end_time": 25544.0,
      "text": "is that often our instincts are wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25544.0,
      "end_time": 28720.0,
      "text": "In the summer of 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28720.0,
      "end_time": 32580.0,
      "text": "there was a massive leak of classified documents"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32580.0,
      "end_time": 35320.0,
      "text": "that came out of the Pentagon."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35320.0,
      "end_time": 36848.0,
      "text": "It shocked the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36848.0,
      "end_time": 38423.0,
      "text": "it shook up the American government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38423.0,
      "end_time": 40576.0,
      "text": "and it made people ask a lot of questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40576.0,
      "end_time": 43257.0,
      "text": "because the sheer amount of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43257.0,
      "end_time": 46832.0,
      "text": "that was let out, and the potential impacts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46832.0,
      "end_time": 49408.0,
      "text": "were significant."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49408.0,
      "end_time": 53430.0,
      "text": "And one of the first questions we asked ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53430.0,
      "end_time": 56147.0,
      "text": "was why would a young soldier have access"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56148.0,
      "end_time": 59800.0,
      "text": "to that much information?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59800.0,
      "end_time": 61605.0,
      "text": "Why would we let sensitive things"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61606.0,
      "end_time": 65764.0,
      "text": "be with a relatively young person?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65764.0,
      "end_time": 68886.0,
      "text": "In the summer of 2003, I was assigned to command"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68886.0,
      "end_time": 71390.0,
      "text": "a special operations task force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71390.0,
      "end_time": 73530.0,
      "text": "and that task force was spread across the Mideast"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73530.0,
      "end_time": 75118.0,
      "text": "to fight al Qaeda."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75118.0,
      "end_time": 78115.0,
      "text": "Our main effort was inside Iraq,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78115.0,
      "end_time": 80820.0,
      "text": "and our specified mission"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80820.0,
      "end_time": 81936.0,
      "text": "was to defeat al Qaeda in Iraq."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81936.0,
      "end_time": 85400.0,
      "text": "For almost five years I stayed there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 86850.0,
      "text": "and we focused on fighting a war"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86850.0,
      "end_time": 91896.0,
      "text": "that was unconventional and it was difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91896.0,
      "end_time": 93736.0,
      "text": "and it was bloody"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93736.0,
      "end_time": 96830.0,
      "text": "and it often claimed its highest price"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96830.0,
      "end_time": 99904.0,
      "text": "among innocent people."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99904.0,
      "end_time": 102408.0,
      "text": "We did everything we could"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102409.0,
      "end_time": 104318.0,
      "text": "to stop al Qaeda"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104318.0,
      "end_time": 107603.0,
      "text": "and the foreign fighters that came in as suicide bombers"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107603.0,
      "end_time": 112717.0,
      "text": "and as accelerants to the violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112718.0,
      "end_time": 114740.0,
      "text": "We honed our combat skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114740.0,
      "end_time": 117576.0,
      "text": "we developed new equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117576.0,
      "end_time": 120290.0,
      "text": "we parachuted, we helicoptered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120300.0,
      "end_time": 122488.0,
      "text": "we took small boats, we drove, and we walked"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122488.0,
      "end_time": 125498.0,
      "text": "to objectives night after night to stop"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125498.0,
      "end_time": 130850.0,
      "text": "the killing that this network was putting forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130850.0,
      "end_time": 133390.0,
      "text": "We bled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133390.0,
      "end_time": 134879.0,
      "text": "we died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134879.0,
      "end_time": 139730.0,
      "text": "and we killed to stop that organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139730.0,
      "end_time": 141472.0,
      "text": "from the violence that they were putting"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141473.0,
      "end_time": 145702.0,
      "text": "largely against the Iraqi people."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145702.0,
      "end_time": 148280.0,
      "text": "Now, we did what we knew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148280.0,
      "end_time": 151194.0,
      "text": "how we had grown up, and one of the things that we knew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151194.0,
      "end_time": 154320.0,
      "text": "that was in our DNA, was secrecy."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154320.0,
      "end_time": 156237.0,
      "text": "It was security. It was protecting information."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156237.0,
      "end_time": 159490.0,
      "text": "It was the idea that information was the lifeblood"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159500.0,
      "end_time": 162690.0,
      "text": "and it was what would protect and keep people safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162690.0,
      "end_time": 164585.0,
      "text": "And we had a sense that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164585.0,
      "end_time": 166596.0,
      "text": "as we operated within our organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166596.0,
      "end_time": 168514.0,
      "text": "it was important to keep information"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168514.0,
      "end_time": 170825.0,
      "text": "in the silos within the organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170825.0,
      "end_time": 173738.0,
      "text": "particularly only give information"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173739.0,
      "end_time": 177931.0,
      "text": "to people had a demonstrated need to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 177931.0,
      "end_time": 182570.0,
      "text": "But the question often came, who needed to know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182570.0,
      "end_time": 185933.0,
      "text": "Who needed, who had to have the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185933.0,
      "end_time": 189400.0,
      "text": "so that they could do the important  parts of the job that you needed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189400.0,
      "end_time": 191550.0,
      "text": "And in a tightly coupled world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 191560.0,
      "end_time": 193854.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s very hard to predict."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 193854.0,
      "end_time": 196798.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very hard to know who needs to have information"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196798.0,
      "end_time": 198305.0,
      "text": "and who doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 198305.0,
      "end_time": 200284.0,
      "text": "I used to deal with intelligence agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200284.0,
      "end_time": 202451.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d complain that they weren&#39;t sharing enough intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202451.0,
      "end_time": 204840.0,
      "text": "and with a straight face, they&#39;d look at me and they&#39;d say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 204841.0,
      "end_time": 206988.0,
      "text": "\"What aren&#39;t you getting?\" (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 206988.0,
      "end_time": 212470.0,
      "text": "I said, \"If I knew that, we wouldn&#39;t have a problem.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 212470.0,
      "end_time": 214720.0,
      "text": "But what we found is we had to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214720.0,
      "end_time": 216249.0,
      "text": "We had to change our culture about information."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216249.0,
      "end_time": 218366.0,
      "text": "We had to knock down walls. We had to share."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218366.0,
      "end_time": 221434.0,
      "text": "We had to change from who needs to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221434.0,
      "end_time": 223557.0,
      "text": "to the fact that who doesn&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 223557.0,
      "end_time": 226791.0,
      "text": "and we need to tell, and tell them as quickly as we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226791.0,
      "end_time": 229917.0,
      "text": "It was a significant culture shift for an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229917.0,
      "end_time": 235241.0,
      "text": "that had secrecy in its DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 235241.0,
      "end_time": 237517.0,
      "text": "We started by doing things, by building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 237517.0,
      "end_time": 239222.0,
      "text": "not working in offices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 239222.0,
      "end_time": 240887.0,
      "text": "knocking down walls, working in things we called"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240887.0,
      "end_time": 243345.0,
      "text": "situation awareness rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 243345.0,
      "end_time": 245821.0,
      "text": "and in the summer of 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 245821.0,
      "end_time": 247444.0,
      "text": "something happened which demonstrated this."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 247444.0,
      "end_time": 249636.0,
      "text": "We captured the personnel records"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249636.0,
      "end_time": 251835.0,
      "text": "for the people who were bringing foreign fighters"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 251836.0,
      "end_time": 253991.0,
      "text": "into Iraq."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 253991.0,
      "end_time": 255839.0,
      "text": "And when we got the personnel records, typically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 255839.0,
      "end_time": 257153.0,
      "text": "we would have hidden these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 257153.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259491.00000000003,
      "text": "shared them with a few intelligence agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 259491.0,
      "end_time": 261286.0,
      "text": "and then try to operate with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 261286.0,
      "end_time": 263325.0,
      "text": "But as I was talking to my intelligence officer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 263325.0,
      "end_time": 264175.0,
      "text": "I said, \"What do we do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 264175.0,
      "end_time": 267201.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Well, you found them.\" Our command."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 267201.0,
      "end_time": 269565.0,
      "text": "\"You can just declassify them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 269565.0,
      "end_time": 271213.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Well, can we declassify them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 271213.0,
      "end_time": 272223.0,
      "text": "What if the enemy finds out?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 272223.0,
      "end_time": 274835.0,
      "text": "And he says, \"They&#39;re their personnel records.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 274835.0,
      "end_time": 276234.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 276235.0,
      "end_time": 277317.0,
      "text": "So we did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277317.0,
      "end_time": 279351.0,
      "text": "and a lot of people got upset about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279351.0,
      "end_time": 281835.0,
      "text": "but as we passed that information around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 281835.0,
      "end_time": 284724.0,
      "text": "suddenly you find that information is only of value"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 284725.0,
      "end_time": 286581.0,
      "text": "if you give it to people who have the ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 286581.0,
      "end_time": 288719.0,
      "text": "to do something with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 288719.0,
      "end_time": 290844.0,
      "text": "The fact that I know something has zero value"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 290845.0,
      "end_time": 292333.0,
      "text": "if I&#39;m not the person who can actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 292333.0,
      "end_time": 294207.0,
      "text": "make something better because of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294207.0,
      "end_time": 296820.0,
      "text": "So as a consequence, what we did was"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 296830.0,
      "end_time": 299193.0,
      "text": "we changed the idea of information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299193.0,
      "end_time": 301477.0,
      "text": "instead of knowledge is power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301477.0,
      "end_time": 304423.0,
      "text": "to one where sharing is power."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 304423.0,
      "end_time": 306395.0,
      "text": "It was the fundamental shift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 306395.0,
      "end_time": 308733.0,
      "text": "not new tactics, not new weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 308733.0,
      "end_time": 310370.0,
      "text": "not new anything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 310370.0,
      "end_time": 312815.0,
      "text": "It was the idea that we were now part of a team"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 312815.0,
      "end_time": 315163.0,
      "text": "in which information became the essential link"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 315163.0,
      "end_time": 319661.0,
      "text": "between us, not a block between us."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 319661.0,
      "end_time": 322243.0,
      "text": "And I want everybody to take a deep breath"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322243.0,
      "end_time": 324365.0,
      "text": "and let it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 324365.0,
      "end_time": 326299.0,
      "text": "because in your life, there&#39;s going to be information"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 326299.0,
      "end_time": 328631.0,
      "text": "that leaks out you&#39;re not going to like."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 328631.0,
      "end_time": 330876.0,
      "text": "Somebody&#39;s going to get my college grades out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 330877.0,
      "end_time": 334904.0,
      "text": "a that&#39;s going to be a disaster. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 334904.0,
      "end_time": 338273.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s going to be okay, and I will tell you that"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 338273.0,
      "end_time": 341493.0,
      "text": "I am more scared of the bureaucrat"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 341493.0,
      "end_time": 343945.0,
      "text": "that holds information in a desk drawer"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343945.0,
      "end_time": 346741.0,
      "text": "or in a safe than I am of someone who leaks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 346741.0,
      "end_time": 349676.0,
      "text": "because ultimately, we&#39;ll be better off if we share."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 349677.0,
      "end_time": 351437.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 351437.0,
      "end_time": 355839.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 357761.0,
      "end_time": 359337.0,
      "text": "Helen Walters: So I don&#39;t know if you were here this morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 359337.0,
      "end_time": 361637.0,
      "text": "if you were able to catch Rick Ledgett,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 361637.0,
      "end_time": 363469.0,
      "text": "the deputy director of the NSA"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 363469.0,
      "end_time": 367133.0,
      "text": "who was responding to Edward Snowden&#39;s talk earlier this week."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 367133.0,
      "end_time": 369445.0,
      "text": "I just wonder, do you think the American government"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 369445.0,
      "end_time": 372133.0,
      "text": "should give Edward Snowden amnesty?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 372133.0,
      "end_time": 374580.0,
      "text": "Stanley McChrystal: I think that Rick said something very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 374581.0,
      "end_time": 377201.0,
      "text": "We, most people, don&#39;t know all the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 377201.0,
      "end_time": 378553.0,
      "text": "I think there are two parts of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 378553.0,
      "end_time": 382293.0,
      "text": "Edward Snowden shined a light on an important need"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 382293.0,
      "end_time": 383783.0,
      "text": "that people had to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 383783.0,
      "end_time": 386765.0,
      "text": "He also took a lot of documents that he didn&#39;t have"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 386765.0,
      "end_time": 389357.0,
      "text": "the knowledge to know the importance of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 389357.0,
      "end_time": 391790.0,
      "text": "so I think we need to learn the facts about this case"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 391790.0,
      "end_time": 393337.0,
      "text": "before we make snap judgments"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 393337.0,
      "end_time": 395485.0,
      "text": "about Edward Snowden."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 395485.0,
      "end_time": 397669.0,
      "text": "HW: Thank you so much. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 397669.0,
      "end_time": 399587.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
